;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_1
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@notice text=Gaol

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_2
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@delevent
@se f=kacha
@wait time=800
@se f=fence
@switchfence x=1 y=6 way=e mode=open
@switchfence x=1 y=4 way=e mode=open
@switchfence x=1 y=3 way=s mode=open
@switchfence x=3 y=7 way=n mode=open
@switchfence x=5 y=9 way=s mode=open
@wait time=1000
@notice text="I heard a door open somewhere!"

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_3
;[exp] true
*event_4
;[exp] true

@delevent
[texton]
When I stepped into what appeared to be a prison cell, I saw a naked girl sitting there looking frightened.[k]
[少女 f=priest_purple_03]「I was being held captive by the vampires of this castle.[r]
You've been a great help, thank you very much.」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>Rescued one girl from captivity!"

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_5
;[exp] true

@delevent
[texton]
When I stepped into what appeared to be a prison cell, I saw a naked girl sitting there looking frightened.[k]
[name n=Carolina f=priest_pink_03]「I was being held captive by the vampires of this castle.[r]
You've been a great help, thank you very much.」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>We rescued Carolina!"
@eval exp='o.娘を助け出してほしい.flag = 1'

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_6
;[exp] true

@delevent
@eval exp='game.curChara = game.party.members.draw()'
[texton]
When I stepped into what appeared to be a prison cell, I saw a naked girl sitting there looking frightened.[k]
[少女 f=witch_blue_02]「I was being held captive by the vampires of this castle.[r]
You've been a great help, thank you very much.」[k]
[if exp='game.curChara.sex == "男"']
	[キャラ f=12]「No, you don't have to thank me... [wait time=500][se f=slash1][nw]Aah![/nw]」[k]
[else]
	[キャラ f=12]「You're welcome... [wait time=500][se f=slash1][nw]Aah![/nw]」[k]
[endif]
Shockingly, the girl bit her supposed rescuer's neck![k]
[少女 f=witch_blue_02]「Hehe! Thanks for the meal ♪」[k]
She sucked a lot of blood from [キャラ]'s neck and quickly walked away.[k]
Apparently, she was a vampire too. We were caught totally caught off guard.[k]
@se f=liquid
@eval exp='game.curChara.life = 1'
[b][nw][キャラ]'s HP decreased significantly![/nw][/b][k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_7
;[exp] map.effect === void

@eval exp='game.map.effect = "PE_storm"'
@eval exp='game.view.startEffect(game.map.effect)'

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_8
;[exp] map.effect == "PE_storm"

@eval exp='game.map.effect = void'
@eval exp='game.view.stopEffect()'

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_9
;[exp] true

[texton]
[if exp='! game.map.events.has(10)']
	[？？？]「I will not allow you to steal my treasure from me...」[k]
[else]
	[？？？]「I will rise again and again... Leave this place quickly...」[k]
[endif]
[リーダー]「...?!」[k]
[textoff]

@wait time=200
@walk move=w
@walk turn=e
@wait time=1000
@se f=roar
@fg c=vampire_white left=450 top=80
@wait time=500
[texton]
[if exp='! game.map.events.has(10)']
	A figure emerged from the darkness and attacked us![k]
[else]
	The vampire lord that we had supposedly defeated earlier came back to life and stood before us![k]
[endif]
[textoff]
@clf

@wait time=500
@monster pos=2 name=バンパイアバット
@monster pos=3 name=ヴァンパイアロード
@monster pos=4 name=バンパイアバット
@callbattle bgm=boss gameover=true
@wait time=500
[texton]
We managed to defeat the vampire lord.[k]
The body of the fallen vampire lord lies at our feet.[k]
...[k]
Could it start moving again? Did we really defeat the vampire lord?[k]
[textoff]
@addevent num=10

[eventoff]
