*event_10
;[exp] onUseEventItem && curItem == o.くい

@eval exp='game.curChara = game.curFighter'
[texton]
[キャラ f=07]「Yaa!」[k]
@se f=slash1
@flash
[キャラ] vigorously plunged the stake into the corpse of the fallen vampire lord![k]
[？？？]「Aaaarghhhh!」[k]
[textoff]
@image layer=e0 storage=PE_base_view mode=psdodge5
@layopt layer=e0 left=0 top=0 visible=true
@startemit layer=e0 storage=PE_powder6 time=1000
@wait time=2000
[texton]
The vampire lord's final screams echoed around him, and soon his body crumbled into tattered ashes and faded into mist.[k]
